## Command 3

**Command Executed:**

```bash
touch ProjectWorkspace/Docs/project_doc.txt
touch ProjectWorkspace/Source/main.c
touch ProjectWorkspace/Backup/backup.txt
```

**Output:**
Files created successfully.

**Observation:**
Three sample files were created in their respective directories for further permission and ownership verification.

